OL,3,CReform UK's first council leader to
OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,FThe UK's first Reform UK council
OL,8,Fleader to formally take office said
OL,9,Fhis party will be able to cut council
OL,10,Ftax as it takes aim at wasteful
OL,11,Fspending.
OL,13,FNew Leicestershire County Council
OL,14,Fleader Dan Harrison said: "To think of
OL,15,Fthe journey from where we came to
OL,16,Fwhere we are, this is just incredible."
