OL,3,CReform UK's first council leader to
OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,FThe former Conservative county
OL,8,Fcouncillor who defected to Reform UK
OL,9,Fin February, is now the party's leader
OL,10,Fin Leicestershire, and was formally
OL,11,Fconfirmed as leader on Wednesday (14
OL,12,FMay).
OL,14,FHe said: "We're now looking at the
OL,15,Fcost, the efficiency, we'll then have
OL,16,Fmoney for front line (services) but
OL,17,Fwe'll also be able to cut council tax."
OL,19,F'Something has got to change' - people
OL,20,Fin Coalville gave their feelings on
OL,21,Fthe new Reform leadership.
