OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,FThe Conservatives lost control of the
OL,8,Fcouncil after 24 years in power, as
OL,9,FReform UK became the largest party.
OL,11,FReform UK holds 25 of Leicestershire's
OL,12,F55 seats compared to the
OL,13,FConservatives' 15.
OL,15,FThe party has opted to govern as a
OL,16,Fminority administration rather than
OL,17,Ftrying to form a coalition with
OL,18,Fanother party.
