OL,3,CReform UK's first council leader to
OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Reform UK in Derbyshire has
OL,8,Fannounced Alan Graves, the former
OL,9,FMayor of Derby, as its new leader
OL,10,Fafter the party unseated the
OL,11,FConservatives across the East Midlands.
OL,13,FAlthough already selected as the
OL,14,Fleader of Derbyshire's largest party,
OL,15,Fhe can only be confirmed as leader of
OL,16,Fthe council at a full council meeting
OL,17,Fon 21 May.
