OL,3,CReform UK's first council leader to
OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,FNigel Farage's party won 42 of the 64
OL,8,FDerbyshire County Council seats,
OL,9,Ftaking overall control away from the
OL,10,FConservatives for the first time in
OL,11,Feight years.
OL,13,FCllr Graves said: "People will see a
OL,14,Fchange, because there'll be more
OL,15,Fpotholes sorted, the roads will be
OL,16,Fbetter, the council efficiency will
OL,17,Ffind money where it once was hidden or
OL,18,Flost and we will achieve great things."
