OL,3,CReform UK's first council leader to
OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,F"We need to make sure the council is
OL,8,Foperating properly and efficiently to
OL,9,Fsee where we can save some of the vast
OL,10,Famounts of money that is being spent."
OL,12,FHe confirmed the party's stance
OL,13,Fagainst net-zero policies, which he
OL,14,Fsaid would be streamlined to those
OL,15,Fwhich would not cost the council extra.
