OL,4,Ctake office promises Leicestershire
OL,5,Ctax cuts
OL,7,FAsked about how the party will tackle
OL,8,Fpotholes and SEND provision, Cllr
OL,9,FGraves said: "I've literally just been
OL,10,Felected and we have not had any
OL,11,Fdiscussions with anybody yet so give
OL,12,Fus a chance to have a chat about it
OL,13,Fand I am sure we might actually come
OL,14,Fup with something."
OL,16,FOf the 42 Reform UK councillors
OL,17,Felected in Derbyshire, none were
OL,18,Fcounty councillors before the election.
